'From Squeak2.6 of 13 October 1999 [latest update: #1727] on 23 December 1999 at 5:06:44 pm'!"Change Set:		FasterChgsSets-arDate:			23 December 1999Author:			Andreas RaabWhen having many change sets (e.g., >= 1000) gathering change sets takes a very long time. This change speeds gathering up by a factor of 25."!!ChangeSorter class methodsFor: 'as yet unclassified' stamp: 'ar 12/23/1999 17:03'!gatherChangeSets	"Collect any change sets created in other projects"	| allChangeSets obsolete |	allChangeSets _ IdentitySet new: AllChangeSets size * 2.	allChangeSets addAll: AllChangeSets.	ChangeSet allSubInstancesDo: [:each |		(allChangeSets includes: each) == (obsolete _ each isMoribund) ifTrue:[			obsolete				ifTrue:[AllChangeSets remove: each]				ifFalse:[AllChangeSets add: each]]].	^ AllChangeSets	"ChangeSorter gatherChangeSets"! !